commit.message: Upgrading surefire, failsafe and checkstyle plugins

files.patch:
@@ -1140,7 +1140,7 @@ under the License.
           <artifactId>openjpa-maven-plugin</artifactId>
           <version>${openjpa.version}</version>
         </plugin>
-        
+
         <plugin>
           <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
           <artifactId>maven-dependency-plugin</artifactId>
@@ -1235,7 +1235,7 @@ under the License.
         <plugin>
           <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
           <artifactId>maven-surefire-plugin</artifactId>
-          <version>2.18.1</version>
+          <version>2.19</version>
           <configuration>
             <redirectTestOutputToFile>true</redirectTestOutputToFile>
             <encoding>utf-8</encoding>
@@ -1246,7 +1246,7 @@ under the License.
         <plugin>
           <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
           <artifactId>maven-failsafe-plugin</artifactId>
-          <version>2.18.1</version>
+          <version>2.19</version>
           <configuration>
             <redirectTestOutputToFile>true</redirectTestOutputToFile>
             <encoding>utf-8</encoding>
@@ -1265,7 +1265,7 @@ under the License.
         <plugin>
           <groupId>org.apache.maven.plugins</groupId>
           <artifactId>maven-checkstyle-plugin</artifactId>
-          <version>2.16</version>
+          <version>2.17</version>
           <configuration>
             <configLocation>${rootpom.basedir}/src/main/resources/org/apache/syncope/checkstyle.xml</configLocation>
             <targetJdk>${targetJdk}</targetJdk>
